{"tid":2207620,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家入嚟睇吓欣師個樣!!!","createTime":"2020-09-18T09:39:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-18T21:12:22.000Z","uid":202833,"like":48,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"4b4dbf01bf1bd6e4231b3676acb89dcf226ddc7a","tid":2207620,"uid":202833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T09:39:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XUctHkZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXUctHkZ.jpg&h=d3c3cdbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">睇吓佢個樣扮黃扮到全世界繼續俾錢佢賺</span></span><br />\n<br />\n咁連登仔可能會話佢篤尿黃啊 冇得揀呀嗎咪揀佢囉<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">咁你哋就錯啦</span></span><br />\n<br />\n因為<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"xx-large\">和你學</span></span>已經上線啦<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"large\">希望大家幫襯返自己人！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家好呀，我係七月嘅時候搞咗個page，<br />\n因為發覺好多中學生都係去嗰啲藍底補習社，<br />\n心諗冇理由仲要比佢哋賺錢，之後就決定咗搞依個page，希望不論學生同老師都可以同聲同氣。<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">唔好比班人食兩家茶飯！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">和你學暫定會捐出每月收入（不扣除成本）嘅五成</span></span>予相關機構（現為612人道支援基金，當然如果有手足想我哋捐俾其他機構都冇問題），希望可以為呢場抗爭一盡綿力。我地會係每月最尾日分別係Facebook同Instagram post上單據。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，如果有學生或者家長想搵私補又咁啱睇到呢個post，可以咁下面條link登記返，我哋就會幫你搵返適合嘅導師！ <br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/rpnaKnH1zVSt2oXw7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FrpnaKnH1zVSt2oXw7&d=U3in%2BbByR8w%2FZmejrHnAdWqRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=23083434\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/rpnaKnH1zVSt2oXw7</a><br />\n<br />\n講漏咗大家可以喺Facebook同IG搵我哋個page!!!<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">Instagram：yellowteach<br />\nFacebook Page：和你學 YellowTeach</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0948693e3cdac33d1428daa5f3ff2a8261a6aa6","tid":2207620,"uid":202833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T09:40:26.000Z","msg":"推比學生手足見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d5211a7282fa3bdfab45a90f03c911bbb76129a","tid":2207620,"uid":202833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T09:40:50.000Z","msg":"如果大家有意見都可以喺呢度同我哋講返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"867fb7ace34a6a47c1e4502d58119f6442739ca9","tid":2207620,"uid":377089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T09:42:05.000Z","msg":"P牌仔推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"588a4050c93a3cbd2b711373aaeb7bdf1bb97887","tid":2207620,"uid":202833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T09:42:18.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76dcaf7d8467b5a8e96a06cd2e536cb4d622070b","tid":2207620,"uid":202833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"867fb7ace34a6a47c1e4502d58119f6442739ca9","tid":2207620,"uid":377089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T09:42:05.000Z","msg":"P牌仔推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T09:42:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1785700d58a68e4f2baae3901308d36b341845d1","tid":2207620,"uid":202833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T09:42:59.000Z","msg":"希望有需要嘅學生可以睇到"},{"pid":"97124415cb0b6a41d675f03fc20502c4f68cfaac","tid":2207620,"uid":202833