理由仲要比佢哋賺錢，之後就決定咗搞依個page，希望不論學生同老師都可以同聲同氣。<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">唔好比班人食兩家茶飯！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">和你學暫定會捐出每月收入（不扣除成本）嘅五成</span></span>予相關機構（現為612人道支援基金，當然如果有手足想我哋捐俾其他機構都冇問題），希望可以為呢場抗爭一盡綿力。我地會係每月最尾日分別係Facebook同Instagram post上單據。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，如果有學生或者家長想搵私補又咁啱睇到呢個post，可以咁下面條link登記返，我哋就會幫你搵返適合嘅導師！ <br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/rpnaKnH1zVSt2oXw7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FrpnaKnH1zVSt2oXw7&d=U3in%2BbByR8w%2FZmejrHnAdWqRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=23083434\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/rpnaKnH1zVSt2oXw7</a><br />\n<br />\n講漏咗大家可以喺Facebook同IG搵我哋個page!!!<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">Instagram：yellowteach<br />\nFacebook Page：和你學 YellowTeach</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T09:57:17.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"901219b0957979307a1f35d1a0fef82b72728053","tid":2207620,"uid":330227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df19130955d28d12c093591dcfcd13c774033a17","tid":2207620,"uid":202833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f29fe574dfcdd6b3e234ab402736812ee0126d88","tid":2207620,"uid":330227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T09:52:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">拉</span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T09:54:18.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">拉佢老味</span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"